The <strong><code>:host</code></strong> <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/CSS">CSS</a> <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Pseudo-classes">pseudo-class</a> selects the shadow host of the <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/Web_Components/Using_shadow_DOM">shadow DOM</a> containing the CSS it is used inside â€” in other words, this allows you select a custom element from inside its shadow DOM.